    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>
                    <sic>Norleans</sic>
                </placeName>
                <date>Oct 15th 1858</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p>Send your Occident to<lb/>
                <persName>Mess D Moore &amp; Co</persName><lb/>
                <placeName>New Orleans</placeName></p>
            <p>I regret to tell you the <sic>epedemic</sic><lb/> still continues &amp; our
                people<lb/> are still falling victims to<lb/> the fell Destroyer</p>
            <p>assistance is now coming in<lb/> which will so far to render aid<lb/> to our various
                Benevolent Societies<lb/>
                <placeName>N York</placeName> has sent to the Genl <add>?</add><lb/> Hebrew
                Benevolent Society.</p>
            <table cols="2" rows="9">
                <row>
                    <cell><persName>L B Can Eq</persName> President</cell>
                    <cell>797.22</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Recd through <persName>Dr J A Cohen</persName></cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>by subscription of a few Israelites</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>at <placeName>Harrisonburg La</placeName></cell>
                    <cell>117.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>recd from <persName>L Klossman</persName> &amp;</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>others from <placeName>Biloxi Miss</placeName></cell>
                    <cell>117.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Recd from <add>?</add>
                        <placeName>Miss</placeName></cell>
                    <cell>50.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>“ <placeName>Clinton La</placeName></cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">75.00</hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>$1156.22</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>Turn over</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <table cols="2" rows="11">
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>1156.22</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>also recd from <placeName>N York</placeName> for the</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Widow &amp; Orphans Home</cell>
                    <cell>250.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Recd from <persName>Dr Liliethenal</persName></cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>&amp; a number of other kind</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Hearted Israelites from</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> &amp; which</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>I also learn goes to the home</cell>
                    <cell>400.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Recd from <placeName>St Louis</placeName> JOBB</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>for General Distribution</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">150.00</hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Total Recd</cell>
                    <cell>$1956 22</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>This assistance will do much good<lb/> but its like a drop of water on the<lb/> sea
                the Hebrew Benevolent<lb/> alone has paid out &amp; incurred an<lb/> expense
                    <sic>allready</sic> of from 3 to $5000<lb/> The Ladies Heb Ben association<lb/>
                has been compelled to Borrow<lb/> $200 in Interest &amp; the Home<lb/> are in Debt
                very largely with<lb/> a large number daily here<lb/> admitted to be fed
                clothed<lb/> &amp; educated yet with all this<lb/> I feel confident we have
                sympathy<lb/> seeing Hearts among you who<lb/> if even late will not be behind<lb/>
                their Brethren in other cities but</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>will yet send their Mite</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Excuse scrawl</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">In Haste yours Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Isaac Hart</persName>
            </p>
            <p><persName>Mr M Goldsmith</persName> has just<lb/> lost one of his children<lb/>
                <persName>Annie</persName> aged 5 years<lb/> and I fear ere 24 Hours he<lb/> will
                lose his only son<lb/> the Doctors fear the worst</p>
            <p>I never knew so much sickness<lb/> in those Born here</p>
        </body>
